{"tid":445042,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好羨慕啲人細細個就知自己以後想做乜⋯⋯","createTime":"2017-10-23T04:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T06:20:02.000Z","uid":5389,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9d0d2729d0975c63436ea9fe31a5490540a1b353","tid":445042,"uid":5389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:23:50.000Z","msg":"唔好話「明白」／「清楚」，你話你知以後想點想做乜，對我嚟講已經好厲害，至少你都有個大方向比你自己跟吖<br />\n<br />\n望返自己，廿七歲仲憨憨鳩鳩咁唔知自己想點<br />\n<br />\n成日聽到啲人話要訂個目標，但連大方向都冇，點跟？<br />\n<br />\n我知自己討厭啲乜，就係唔知自己鍾意／想做啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa3ae40a7b65510dec06d3a2c52c466e57105f9","tid":445042,"uid":73404,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:26:42.000Z","msg":"諗得太多<br />\n做得太少<br />\n又唔洗愁既 <br />\n絕大部分人都係煮到埋黎就食咁過世架唔"},{"pid":"ec045f65818969a4f8dbd2c0b826c2a5ae030cfb","tid":445042,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:26:42.000Z","msg":"我想快d退休唔駛做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c291fb8faf923ae641724d9f63a1c37fbca503","tid":445042,"uid":5389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:32:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗得太多<br />\n做得太少<br />\n又唔洗愁既 <br />\n絕大部分人都係煮到埋黎就食咁過世架唔</blockquote><br />\n飯來張口我都想，煩少好多嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73bbceede22a0aeeca4b7417625074f465b3f569","tid":445042,"uid":5389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:34:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想快d退休唔駛做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我連想打咩工都煩惱緊，你同我講退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ae659096e88c8f52b4e3bf6388c240c278824e","tid":445042,"uid":115150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb40921ee5ca805e3c1b97cb2cf41044f77ce50","tid":445042,"uid":5389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:36:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec1e814643ba0ab9a6e5fe109756c7f260d5006","tid":445042,"uid":40908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一樣27歲on99<br />\n仲成日想裸辭，但無父幹手停口停<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b62ee78b965f547b89eda5b3af2005cc2f7388","tid":445042,"uid":138375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:40:15.000Z","msg":"知同唔知都有好有唔好既<br />\n總好過知但係做唔到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a6a016afa04c96056bafdbe9a87039278dd0a69","tid":445042,"uid":5389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:50:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一樣27歲on99<br />\n仲成日想裸辭，但無父幹手停口停<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打 God bless you<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說，做盛行搞到妳咁煩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae3139af3608ce1b7018d1908f65f5a62dcc18e","tid":445042,"uid":5389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:57:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>知同唔知都有好有唔好既<br />\n總好過知但係做唔到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但至少，「知道自己想點」係第一步囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早有早做，遲有遲做，KFC上校都係頭髮白晒先創辦KFC啫（唔知點解由細記到依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n我連呢個「第一步」都猶豫不決<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2463123c4f52e936212534ad0c152c615439f031","tid":445042,"uid":40908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T05:59:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一樣27歲on99<br />\n仲成日想裸辭，但無父幹手停口停<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打 God bless you<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說，做盛行搞到妳咁煩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nb2b sales，做左無耐<br />\n煩就知份份工都煩架啦<br />\n但真係諗唔到自己想做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對好多野都無興趣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b202c004a28a08453cf26931476ee32f4632c0f1","tid":445042,"uid":5389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T06:20:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一樣27歲on99<br />\n仲成日想裸辭，但無父幹手停口停<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打 God bless you<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說，做盛行搞到妳咁煩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nb2b sales，做左無耐<br />\n煩就知份份工都煩架啦<br />\n但真係諗唔到自己想做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對好多野都無興趣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一樣係知自己唔鍾意／討厭啲乜，但又唔知自己鍾意啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我依家就做緊地盤（大判），當日衰心急入咗行<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不過應該會呢個禮拜內辭職，做撚到成隻狗咁，但啲上司只係會話：「未撚夠狗呀，再狗啲啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n屌你下世都唔會再做地盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}